{"tid":682880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小巴壞冷氣 司機疑暈倒斜路衝行半公里 連撞5車3人傷","createTime":"2018-05-29T08:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T08:44:09.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca31303ff9d2dba5282a07d658941b0f24246e3","tid":682880,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:20:38.000Z","msg":"青衣寮肚路發生6車「串燒」交通意外。下午1時，專線小巴407線落斜途中失事，連撞前面及對面線車輛，包括私家車、的士、電單車、小巴及巴士，最少3人受傷。現場消息稱，小巴司機行駛途中暈倒肇事，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n被撞的其中一部小巴409線，司機稱當時他沿寮肚路上斜綠燈行車，「見到對面架407衝着落，車速40至50，唔算快，但冇減速」，在長亨邨車場出入口撞低電單車，再越過雙白撞過來，先後撞其小巴及的士，再返回原來行車線撞客貨車和巴士。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查得悉，小巴在寮肚路斜路頂已經失事，剷上迴旋處撞兩個路牌及燈箱後再衝行，全程約600米。<br />\n<br />\n讀者黎先生途經現場，見到電單車和頭盔跌在地上，鐵騎士由其他人扶到行人路，神智清醒。黎其後聽到其他小巴司機稱，肇事小巴冷氣壞掉，懷疑司機在車上中暑暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180529/large/1527574202_db69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180529%2Flarge%2F1527574202_db69.jpg&h=bc1bc4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">鐵騎士倒地受傷。(讀者提供)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180529/large/1527575628_385d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180529%2Flarge%2F1527575628_385d.jpg&h=4b239647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">迴旋處上的兩個路牌及燈箱被撞爛。(梁瑞帆攝)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚熱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180529/58251152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F58251152&d=Z8UvfzV38QS9GCWS0GEfHdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=836242b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F58251152&h=d1ce659e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180529/58251152</a>"},{"pid":"923a6029294e8af0f607b7109ab1200b38e36f28","tid":682880,"uid":4575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:23:02.000Z","msg":"支持關冷氣日"},{"pid":"181a7d951b528bfa560938c6a5d192a26b36913e","tid":682880,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"今日咁多串燒撞車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bf517fe622b551480f9ad807f16b375e61820b","tid":682880,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d3ca974ad671e5485e4e4f8aa2c0e7419a5171","tid":682880,"uid":185953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"再次證明咁熱根本唔應該翻工"},{"pid":"219d349b07c8411e3bde5069e3b4ce2c0b2fcba3","tid":682880,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"渣ga"}]}